{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dd9cf6d6b3","title":"中共中央关于对去台人员在大陆亲属政策的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ad1891619a","index":0,"year":1979,"month":11,"day":1,"articleId":"dd9cf6d6b3","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对港台关系","id":"1f3b70f4a2","type":"主题"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"中共中央通知","id":"91736a0628","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"对文革的评价和政策","id":"d8ee3d1fe9","type":"主题"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f0851990bd","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于对去台人员在大陆亲属政策的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd9cf6d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"85f7afa416","type":"paragraph","text":"各省、市、自治区党委，中央各部委，国家机关各部委党组，各人民团体党组，总政治部：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd9cf6d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a369b20d1d","type":"paragraph","text":"对待去台人员在大陆的亲属，党中央曾制定了明确政策，但遭到林彪、“四人帮”严重破坏。现重申如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd9cf6d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"05679ded42","type":"paragraph","text":"一、对去台人员在大陆的亲属，应在政治、经济、社会生活等方面，一视同仁，平等相待，不得歧视。台湾是中国的地方，不能把在台湾的亲友说咸是“海外关系”。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd9cf6d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d07ee970b","type":"paragraph","text":"二、大陆和台湾亲友间正常的通信、通电，任何人不得干预。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd9cf6d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"de7ee72db9","type":"paragraph","text":"三、去台人员在大陆的亲属，遭到林彪、“四人帮”政治陷害的，一律平反。迫害致死的，应予昭雪。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd9cf6d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d73e956806","type":"paragraph","text":"四、对去台人员在大陆亲属的团结教育和落实政策工作，请各省、市、自治区党委先在党内进行宣传教育，然后安排落实。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd9cf6d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"efd33a8ed6","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd9cf6d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"70a242db7a","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七九年十一月一日","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd9cf6d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}